#~ msgid "Saurian Headhunter"
#~ msgstr "Cacciatore di teste sauro"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Saurian Headhunters are the heavy fighters of the saurians. Armed with an "
#~ "axe, they can deliver relatively strong blows, but are encumbered by "
