#~ "defense of the border towns and villages.  They are drawn from the ranks "
#~ "of veteran soldiers, not nobility, and all have shown leadership and "
#~ "courage in battle."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "I comandanti della fanteria di Wesnoth sono responsabili delle "
