#~ "ancient dwarf. The tomb seems empty except for this ornate stone coffin. "
#~ "The skeleton inside the coffin has long since vanished into dust. All "
#~ "that's left are a few ceremonial trinkets and this shining golden belt. "
#~ "Inscribed on this inside are the words: 'May you have the toughness to "
#~ "stay standing long after your enemies fall'  Grave robbing is never a "
#~ "good thing to do, but this belt looks magical and its former owner "
#~ "certainly won't miss it."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "In base alle rune che coprono i muri questa deve essere la tomba di "
