#~ "Wait, my people, do not be deceived. This thing that appears by "
#~ "Tanstafaal's side is not our god. I too was fooled at first, but I have "
#~ "come to realize by her actions that she is an imposter. When she appeared "
#~ "to me the night before Garak died, she told me to kill all that lived "
#~ "under the mountains, even the dwarves who ended up helping us. Likewise "
#~ "when we escaped from the caves, she appeared to me again, and told me to "
#~ "bow down to the humans, else she would destroy me. Never has Eloh "
#~ "threatened one of us or dictated our actions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Aspettate, gente, non fatevi ingannare. L'essere che appare al fianco di "
