#~ msgid ""
#~ "Why should we trust you? We have not heard Eloh's words directly. Only "
#~ "now that you have led us into this folly has Eloh appeared to us."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Perché dovremmo fidarci di te? Non abbiamo sentito le parole di Eloh "
#~ "direttamente. Solo adesso che ci hai condotto in questa pazzia ci è "
#~ "apparsa Eloh."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "She claims to be the one who has shepherded us during his journey, but "
#~ "who protected you across the harsh sands, who fought the orcs and led you "
